-- Bouygues to Build AEK Larnaca Football Stadium, Inbusiness Says
-- B y   S t e l i o s   O r p h a n i d e s
-- 2012-01-19T10:57:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-19/bouygues-to-build-aek-larnaca-football-stadium-inbusiness-says.html
Bouygues Batiment International SA’s
Cyprus unit will construct a new stadium for  AEK Larnaca ’s
football club, Inbusiness reported today, without citing anyone.  The cost, including training facilities and a commercial
center, will exceed 30 million euros ($39 million) and will be
subsidized by as much as 7 million euros from the state-
sponsored  Cyprus Sports Organization , the web-based newspaper
said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stelios Orphanides in Nicosia at  sorphanides@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at   cstirling1@bloomberg.net  